If you’re looking for some recipe inspiration to change up your meal routine, you’ve come to the right place. We’ve gathered June’s most-liked recipes that were shared on the HuffPost Taste Instagram account (which you should follow!), and this month’s list is guaranteed to introduce you to a new favourite. From virtuous dishes like mango chopped salad to more sumptuous recipes like butter Old Bay crab mac and cheese, there’s a good mix to suit whatever you’re craving.